<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AI Learning Certificate</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e2b3a, #0f1a24);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-family: 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .certificate {
            background: #fef8e7;
            background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 10% 20%, rgba(215, 185, 115, 0.05) 2%, transparent 2.5%);
            background-size: 28px 28px;
            width: 850px;
            max-width: 100%;
            padding: 50px 40px;
            border: 12px double #b8860b;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3), 0 0 0 8px #fef8e7, 0 0 0 14px #b8860b;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .certificate::before {
            content: "🏅";
            font-size: 50px;
            position: absolute;
            top: -30px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            background: #fef8e7;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-family: 'Impact', 'Arial Black', sans-serif;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            color: #3b2a1f;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #d4af37;
            display: inline-block;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #5a3e1b;
            margin: 15px 0 25px;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .presented {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: 20px 0 10px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .recipient {
            font-size: 44px;
            font-family: 'Brush Script MT', cursive, serif;
            color: #9b4b1a;
            margin: 15px 0;
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #c28a3e, #8b5a2b);
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            color: #8b5a2b;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .achievement {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin: 20px 30px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            border-left: 4px solid #d4af37;
            border-right: 4px solid #d4af37;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            background: #fffcf0;
        }

        .achievement p {
            margin: 8px 0;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .signatures {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px dashed #b8860b;
        }

        .signature {
            text-align: center;
            width: 40%;
        }

        .signature .line {
            width: 200px;
            max-width: 100%;
            height: 2px;
            background: #3b2a1f;
            margin: 10px auto;
        }

        .date {
            margin-top: 25px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #3b2a1f;
            font-family: monospace;
        }

        .stamp {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 50px;
            right: 60px;
            opacity: 0.7;
            font-size: 55px;
            transform: rotate(-15deg);
            font-family: monospace;
            color: #b8860b;
            border: 3px double #b8860b;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #fef8e7;
        }

        @media (max-width: 650px) {
            .certificate { padding: 30px 20px; }
            h1 { font-size: 32px; }
            .recipient { font-size: 32px; }
            .stamp { font-size: 35px; bottom: 20px; right: 20px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="certificate">
        <h1>🏆 CERTIFICATE OF ACHIEVEMENT</h1>
        <div class="subtitle">Official Recognition for AI Engineering Efforts</div>

        <div class="presented">This certificate is proudly presented to</div>
        <div class="recipient">Mahtab (The Debugger)</div>

        <div class="achievement">
            <strong>★ for successfully completing the Day of Real AI Learning ★</strong>
            <p>✓ Installed and used external Python libraries (requests).</p>
            <p>✓ Mastered PATH troubleshooting & command-line debugging.</p>
            <p>✓ Fixed API errors: Model decommissioned → switched to working models.</p>
            <p>✓ Understood API keys, headers, status codes, and JSON responses.</p>
            <p>✓ Ran first AI agent with Groq API and built confidence to experiment.</p>
            <p>★ PROGRESS: From "copy-paste" to active debugging & code modification.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="signatures">
            <div class="signature">
                <div class="line"></div>
                <strong>AI Mentor</strong><br>
                <span style="font-size:12px">Groq AI Assistant</span>
            </div>
            <div class="signature">
                <div class="line"></div>
                <strong>Learner's Proof</strong><br>
                <span style="font-size:12px">Self-attested effort</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="date">
            🗓️ Issued: June 1, 2026 &nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp; ✅ 100% Guarantee of Completion
        </div>

        <div class="stamp">
            ✔️ SEAL
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
